NK125(co)005:1: // shar kah thog pa bsod nams rgyal mtshan gyi rnam par thar pa bzhugs so //
NK125(co)005:3: gdod nas dag pa'i chos sku nam mkha' yangs pa las /
NK125(co)005:4: lhun grub 'gag med chu 'dzin rab 'khrigs shing //
NK125(co)005:5: sna tshogs sprul pa 'gro la chu rgyun 'bebs //
NK125(co)005:6: rtsa brgyud bla ma rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK125(co)005:7: sku gsum rgyal ba kun gyi rnam 'phrul las //
NK125(co)005:8: theg gsum chos kyi dpal 'byor yongs kyis phyug /
NK125(co)005:9: khams gsum 'gro ba'i dbul 'phongs sel mdzad pa'i //
NK125(co)005:10: bka' drin 'khor med rje la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK125(co)005:12: sa gsum na 'dran zla dang bral ba /
NK125(co)005:13: dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyi thugs sras /
NK125(co)005:14: thos bsam sgom pa'i gtsug rgyan /
NK125(co)005:15: mdo rgyud bstan pa'i mnga' bdag /
NK125(co)005:16: khyad par o rgyan chen pos lung bstan zhing /
NK125(co)005:18: pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi rgyal tshab du byon pa /
NK125(co)005:20: ma rig mun sel thugs rje'i bdag nyid /
NK125(co)005:21: mtshan nyi zla ltar yongs su grags pa /
NK125(co)005:22: kahthoga rin po che bsod nams rgyal mtshan dpal bzang po zhes /
NK125(co)005:23: smon lam gyi dbang gis bod kyi yul mdo khams su sku 'khrungs kyang /
NK125(co)005:24: gdul bya'i zhing dbus gtsang lho bod du byon te /
NK125(co)005:25: bstan pa'i 'dzin skyong spel gsum rnams dar rgyas su mdzad do //
NK125(co)005:26: skyes bu dam pa de ni chung nas rab tu byung zhing thos bsam gyis chos la sbyangs tshul /
NK125(co)005:27: bar du mkhas grub mang du bsten nas gdams pa'i bcud ma lus pa gsan zhing /
NK125(co)005:28: dka' spyad sdug sgur mdzad nas bsgoms bsgrub bskyed rdzogs kyi don la sbyangs tshul /
NK125(co)005:29: mthar gzhan phan thugs bskyed kyis 'gro don /
NK125(co)005:30: 'chad rtsod brtsom gsum la ma rmongs pas /
NK125(co)005:31: gdul bya rnams kyi re ba so sor bskongs te /
NK125(co)005:32: dbang bskur rab gnas kyi dus su byin rlabs kyi rtags mtshan /
NK125(co)005:33: 'phrin las 'gro ba 'dul don ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba gzhan yid ches pa ston pa sogs /
NK125(co)005:34: rnam thar bsdus pa tsam zhal rgyun ji lta ba bzhin /
NK125(co)005:35: dri med yid bzhin gyi nor bu'i phreng ba'i nang du ston te /
NK125(co)005:36: zhib tu gsang ba'i rnam thar bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro rnams kyi zhal gzigs rnams dang /
NK125(co)005:37: bsnyen bsgrub mdzad pa'i skabs su /
NK125(co)005:38: dngos nyams kyi rtags khyad par can dang /
NK125(co)005:39: lung bstan la sogs mang du yod gsung snang ste /
NK125(co)005:40: nan gyis zhus kyang bka' ma grol bas yi ger ma bkod /
NK125(co)005:41: 'dir mya ngan las 'das pa'i mdzad pa /
NK125(co)005:42: gdul bya zhing khams gzhan du gshegs pa'i tshul mdo
NK125(co)005:43: tsam cig kho bo rnam grol ming can gyis 'bri
NK125(co)005:44: bar bya ste / rtsa ba gsum gyis rjes su gnang du gsol /
NK125(co)005:45: rje rin po che 'di nyid ni sprul pa yar
NK125(co)005:46: 'gyed kyi sangs rgyas gang la gang 'dul du byon
NK125(co)005:47: pa / bsam bzhin du skye ba bzhes pa ste /
NK125(co)005:49: nyon mongs zad par gyur kyang skye ba ston par byed /
NK125(co)005:50: rgas dang na dang 'chi ba med kyang 'chi 'pho ston /
NK125(co)005:52: sprul pa sna tshogs su 'gyed nus shing 'byin 'jug
NK125(co)005:53: gnas gsum la rang dbang thob pa'i skyes chen du
NK125(co)005:54: mchis na'ang / gdul bya rtags 'dzin can rnams sun 'byin pa dang /
NK125(co)005:55: le lo can rnams la bskul ma 'debs phyir dang /
NK125(co)005:56: 'dus byas kyi chos thams cad mi rtag pa'i brda'
NK125(co)005:57: sprod pa'i phyir du mya ngan las 'da' ba'i tshul
NK125(co)005:59: sangs rgyas mya ngan yongs mi 'da' //
NK125(co)005:60: chos kyang nub par mi 'gyur te //
NK125(co)005:61: ma rig smin mdzad 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK125(co)005:62: byung nas mya ngan 'da' bar ston ces gsungs te /
NK125(co)005:63: don gyi ngo bor ni gshegs bzhugs mi mnga' 'o //
NK125(co)005:64: de yang bsnyen bsgrub kyi skabs su /
NK125(co)005:65: dgung lo bdun bcu don gnyis thub pa mkha' 'gros lung bstan byung ba las /
NK125(co)005:66: dam pa de nyid ni bya dka' ba khyad du bsad cing /
NK125(co)005:67: sdug bsngal la ji mi snyam gyis bzod pa'i go cha bgos te /
NK125(co)005:68: bstan pa dang sems can gyi don du 'gyur na rang gi sku srog la'ang mi 'phangs pa'i /
NK125(co)005:69: byang chub sems dpa' chen po'i rlabs po che la lhod pa med par rgyun du gnas shing /
NK125(co)005:70: sku tshe'i stod rnams su dka' spyad sdug sgur sbas yul 'byed pa'i thugs rtsol sogs /
NK125(co)005:71: ltar snang shin tu 'o brgyal ba'i rnam pa la brten nas /
NK125(co)005:72: sku tshe'i smad la sku grang gi rnam pas sku
NK125(co)005:73: grib la brten pa'i yang yang du bsnyel 'dug pa
NK125(co)005:74: / phyis stag tshang o rgyan rtse mo nang du sku mtshams la bzhugs shing /
NK125(co)005:75: phyogs nas mjal mkhan gal che ba byung dus zhal mjal cung zad dang /
NK125(co)005:76: de mtshon rnams la yol ba phyi nang gi gsung
NK125(co)005:77: mjal sogs skabs dang sbyar nas gnang ba yod dus
NK125(co)005:79: gnas skabs su lus rten gcig blangs gzhir bzhag la /
NK125(co)005:80: 'byung ba las grub pa yin pas /
NK125(co)005:81: na tsha la sogs los yong /
NK125(co)005:82: nga ma tshad rnying ma phyogs bsgrub brgyud kyi bla ma /
NK125(co)005:83: sa skya pa phyogs kyi bshad brgyud /
NK125(co)005:84: bka' brgyud phyogs kyi sgom brgyud kyi bla ma gong
NK125(co)005:85: ma mkhas grub rnams la'ang snyung ba dang 'das tshul
NK125(co)005:88: de la bdag gis 'di lta zhus ste /
NK125(co)005:89: bla ma dge ba'i bshes gnyen thugs sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa dang khyad med pa la /
NK125(co)005:92: sku gzugs bzang ngan sogs mi 'dra ba mang du 'byung bar 'dug cing /
NK125(co)005:93: nged rang gi rje rin po che ni dus phyis
NK125(co)005:94: sku khams brnyel ba kho na yong 'dug pa 'di
NK125(co)005:96: 'o de shin tu 'ong bar 'dug /'di dag thams
NK125(co)005:97: cad tshe sngan ma'i 'phen pa bzang ngan kyang yin
NK125(co)005:98: / smon lam gyi stobs kyang yin /
NK125(co)005:99: rgyu 'bras slu ba med pa ni /
NK125(co)005:100: sngon thub pa rin po che la'ang bdud mi nag mdung thugs can bsad pa'i rnam smin las /
NK125(co)005:101: zhabs la tsan+dana gyi tshal pa zug ces gsungs pas /
NK125(co)005:102: nga yang rang rgyud pa rang cung min te /
NK125(co)005:103: gnas skabs kyi na tsha 'di shin tu yod par 'dug /
NK125(co)005:104: tshe 'di mi dge sdig pa'i las byas pa gcig ma dran te /
NK125(co)005:106: gal te nyams la rtags med na //
NK125(co)005:107: legs par snang ba mi rung ste //
NK125(co)005:108: bde ba zad byas gtan du sdug /
NK125(co)005:109: gal te nyams la rtags byung na //
NK125(co)005:110: sngon gyi rnam smin zad 'gyur bas //
NK125(co)005:111: bskang gso'i las la brtson par bya //
NK125(co)005:113: rnam smin las kyi lhag ro rnams dag 'gro ba yin las che /
NK125(co)005:114: 'on kyang na tsha rnams dge sbyor gyi grogs su 'gro tsam 'dug /
NK125(co)005:115: las rgyu 'bras slu ba med pa rje thams cad mkhyen pa'i khyad chos yin gsung /
NK125(co)005:116: de ltar dgung lo bdun bcu don gnyis yan chod du snyung ba las /
NK125(co)005:117: na tsha yang yang du yong ba 'dug te /
NK125(co)005:118: nga rang gi tshe tshad la ni cung ma sleb gsung /
NK125(co)005:119: de nas khyi lo shar te bdun bcu don gsum dgung snying gi stengs su phebs pa'i tshe /
NK125(co)005:120: sku khams snyel po byung ste bdag rnams kyang bod phyogs su yod dus gcig la /
NK125(co)005:121: mgyogs myur shog gsung pa'i bka' shog yang yang phebs te /
NK125(co)005:123: sku khams kyang yar sos su byung 'dug /
NK125(co)005:124: de dus mnga' ris pa chos rje kun rnam pa
NK125(co)005:125: zhes pa dpon slob kyang gsung chos zhur byung ste
NK125(co)005:127: nges skyi khrid byed gsung nas /
NK125(co)005:128: dgongs pa zang thal gyi khrid gnang ngo //
NK125(co)005:129: gzhan yang phyogs nas dge ba'i bshes gnyen mang po
NK125(co)005:130: mjal byon pa rnams dang rang gi grwa slob sogs
NK125(co)005:131: la / so sor chos kyis tshim par mdzad do //
NK125(co)005:132: de nas phag lo shar ba'i tshe /
NK125(co)005:133: bod phyogs nas rang re'i bu chen chos rje 'jam dpal ba sogs /
NK125(co)005:134: 'bring mtshams mgo yul phyogs kyi grwa bu slob thams cad 'dus te /
NK125(co)005:135: 'bul ba'i bye brag kyang dpag med phul /
NK125(co)005:136: gsol 'debs gdan bzhugs kho na la gtso bor 'bad pa ston /
NK125(co)005:137: bdag dpon slob rnams ni shar phyogs su 'gro dgos pa byung /
NK125(co)005:138: rje gong nas dgun stod phyogs nas 'dus pa /
NK125(co)005:139: gsung chos khrid rgyas par gnang zhing /
NK125(co)005:141: khyed rang tsho 'dir sdod gang khom gyis la sdod /
NK125(co)005:142: nga yang yun ring bsdad pa'i nges pa med /
NK125(co)005:143: the tshom gyi dri ba dgos pa rnams kyang dris shig /
NK125(co)005:144: sang nyams len byed pa'i dus /
NK125(co)005:145: gnyis 'dzin the tshom gyi dra bar tshud na mi btub cing /
NK125(co)005:146: sgro 'dogs gcod dgos pa rnams chod /
NK125(co)005:147: phyis nas nga dran po yong gsung /
NK125(co)005:148: der 'tshogs pa thams cad kyis rang rang gi the tshom zhus /
NK125(co)005:149: rje yis dgongs don thams cad bkrol nas gnad 'dug go //
NK125(co)005:150: yang dgun smad phyogs su shin tu sku khams dub par gyur te /
NK125(co)005:151: bdag shar du yod dus shog gsung nas myur bar 'ongs te gnas chen du /
NK125(co)005:152: zhabs drung 'jal tshe shin tu bsnyel ba'i tshul du
NK125(co)005:153: 'dug dus sku rim dos drag cing stobs che ba
NK125(co)005:157: sbyin bsreg bskang bshags grib sel /
NK125(co)005:158: gsung sgrog sogs bsgrub pas zhing du ma gshegs tsam byung /
NK125(co)005:159: de dang mtshungs par chos sding nas chos rje bsgrub
NK125(co)005:160: chen pa dpon slob rnams mjal bar phebs pas 'bul
NK125(co)005:162: dam tshig gtsang zhing lhag bsam rnam par dag pa'i
NK125(co)005:163: mos gus gdung ba drag pos gsol ba phur tshugs
NK125(co)005:165: legs tshogs kyi rten 'brel du ma nas 'grig te /
NK125(co)005:166: sku khams kyang yar sos byung /
NK125(co)005:167: der rjes chos rje rdo rje ba sogs la stod
NK125(co)005:168: phyogs kyi bu slob dbu mdzad rdo rje dbang phyug
NK125(co)005:169: / dbu mdzad dge 'dun rgya mtsho sogs bod kyi gra slob rnams kyang 'dus te /
NK125(co)005:170: rang rang gi dngos po ci yod rnams kyang phul /
NK125(co)005:172: gdam pa'i lhag lus rnams kyang zhus so //
NK125(co)005:173: bla ma bsod nams bzang gis kyang rong phyogs kyi 'bul bsdud 'khor te /
NK125(co)005:174: ja sig gos dar sogs brjod kyi mi lang ba phul ste phyag phyi bsgrub pa'i mthil mdzad /
NK125(co)005:175: lho phyogs kyi yang bla ma bu chen rnams dang /
NK125(co)005:176: dgon pa 'dzin pa'i bla ma bskos pa dang gsar dgon pa /
NK125(co)005:180: rdo khra lcag zam thog kha /
NK125(co)005:182: ra rgod brag sogs kyi gdan sa rang rang gi 'khor 'bangs rnams dang bcas /
NK125(co)005:183: 'bul ba'i bye brag dpag med thogs nas mjal bar 'dus te /
NK125(co)005:184: rang rang blos kyi zhu ba rnams kyang zhus /
NK125(co)005:186: gdams pa ngo sprod sogs kyang thugs mdzod brtol ste gnang ngo //
NK125(co)005:187: de'i tshe skabs gcig zhal nas /
NK125(co)005:188: da lan khyed tshos rkyen bzlog rims 'gro sogs kyang brtson par byung pas /
NK125(co)005:190: ya ma'i nor longs spyod rnams sbyin gtong byas pa rmis /
NK125(co)005:191: da lo rang dga' mo yong ba 'dra gsung /
NK125(co)005:192: dge bsnyen nyi shu rtsa gcig byung nas nga dang ldan gcig tu nyal song /
NK125(co)005:193: nad yun ring tsam le yong yin /
NK125(co)005:194: de dus gzigs snang dpag tu med pa byung 'dug ste /
NK125(co)005:196: de nas sku khams kyang mus kyis dngas te de'i ston sku khams kyang bzang po byung /
NK125(co)005:197: stag tshang bsgrub mchod tshugs te /
NK125(co)005:198: mjal mkhan yang shin tu mang ba byung /
NK125(co)005:199: bsgrub dbang gi skabs gcig tu /
NK125(co)005:200: bdag sku mdun du phyin te 'di ltar zhus so //
NK125(co)005:201: deng sang mjal mkhan mang ba dang /
NK125(co)005:202: sku grib bzhin gyis sku khams nyog pa ma byung lags sam zhes snyung gsos sogs zhus pas /
NK125(co)005:203: rje'i zhal nas mi mang ba'i stobs kyis khams cung zad nyog pa 'dug ste /
NK125(co)005:204: 'on kyang dus phyis khyod yod pa des dbang dang byin rlabs byed ma dgos pas /
NK125(co)005:205: khyad chen po byung gsung nas dgyes pa'i tshul mdzad /
NK125(co)005:206: bsgrub chen gyi dus su 'pho ba'i zhal gdam thor bu'ang 'ga' re gnang /
NK125(co)005:207: gsang sngags lag len gyi che ba yin gsung /
NK125(co)005:208: de sang gzigs snang rnal lam bzhin ci ltar byung zhus pas /
NK125(co)005:209: rmi lam rtag thub rang ma byung ste /
NK125(co)005:210: zhag gnyis gsum gyi gong tho rang kha gcig la /
NK125(co)005:211: 'di ltar nga nyid dpal 'bras mo bshongs yin zer ba'i /
NK125(co)005:212: sngar sleb pa'i sa dang yang mi 'dra ba /
NK125(co)005:213: sa gzhi nyams dga' zhing lhun chags pa /
NK125(co)005:215: mtha' skor rtsi shing nags tshal me tog /
NK125(co)005:216: ma smos pa'i lo tog rnams kyang bkra ba yid du 'ong ba'i gnas gcig tu sleb 'dug pas /
NK125(co)005:217: mkha' 'gro ma yin zer ba mang pos tshogs kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK125(co)005:218: mi ma yin gzhi bdag yin zer ba rnams kyis kyang gus 'dud byed pa zhig byung /
NK125(co)005:219: 'on kyang snga thog gi bag chags yin las che gsung /
NK125(co)005:220: da dung bsams na zhing khams su gshegs pa'i mkha' 'gro sus mar 'dug /
NK125(co)005:221: khyed rang tsho yang gnas de phyogs su 'dzin spras shed gang chug dgos rgyu yin /
NK125(co)005:222: deng sang nga 'dras pher ba yin na pha khyim du bu 'gro ba lta bu gcig yod de /
NK125(co)005:223: las 'phro smon lam gyi dbang gis 'di phyogs su lus la gcig byung /
NK125(co)005:225: 'bras mo bshongs la 'gro ba'i zhal gdam dang /
NK125(co)005:226: nub sgo nas 'jug pa'i zhal gdams kyi shog bkra gcig kyang gnang byung /
NK125(co)005:227: nga'i rjes 'jug rnams 'bras mo bshongs dang stag tshang gnyis su rten chos shig gsung /
NK125(co)005:228: der rjes nub gcig sku mdun du shog la sdod gsung ste bsdad pas /
NK125(co)005:229: nub zangs te khyod kyang phar tshur 'gro dgos mang /
NK125(co)005:231: lo rgyus 'di rnams sems la zhog gsungs /
NK125(co)005:232: spyir 'das ma 'ongs da ltar dus gsum kyi zhal bkod gnang zhing /
NK125(co)005:233: kah thog gi dam pa bde gshegs nas man /
NK125(co)005:234: ye shes rgyal mtshan yan chad kyi rnam thar dang /
NK125(co)005:235: lhag par ye shes 'bum pa zhing du gshegs pa nas dgongs rdzogs bsgrub tshul rnams rgyas par gnang /
NK125(co)005:236: bar skabs gcig tu dge rtsa gang las kyang /
NK125(co)005:237: ma ni dung phyur tshul ldan byung na de rang phan yon che gsung ste /
NK125(co)005:238: dus dang bstun pas nyer cag mi dgos pa /
NK125(co)005:239: dge ba'i rtsa ba yang dag pa ste /
NK125(co)005:240: da lo de ra nga dung phyur gcig mi 'grub gsung /
NK125(co)005:241: bdag gis da lo rang cung mi 'grub lags sam /
NK125(co)005:242: grags yul sta gon kyang ci yang med lags zhus pas /
NK125(co)005:245: ji ltar gsungs pa thams cad zhal chems kyi rnam yang 'dra ste /
NK125(co)005:246: sems can bsod nams dman pas zhing 'di nas gshegs pa ni nges par 'byung /
NK125(co)005:247: de'i tshe dgongs pa ma ni rang rdzogs pa 'dra snyam pa byung /
NK125(co)005:248: yang bdag gis rje nyid gshegs pa lta bu byung na /
NK125(co)005:249: bdag bu slob rnams kyis blo gtad su la re ji ltar bgyi zhus pas /
NK125(co)005:250: kye ma 'chi ba byas kyang rnam rtog yin //
NK125(co)005:251: don la 'chi byed spros dang bral //
NK125(co)005:252: gnas skabs mkha' 'gro'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK125(co)005:254: chos sku rnam par dag pa la //
NK125(co)005:255: chos sku la ni chos sku thim //
NK125(co)005:256: de la 'chi ba'i tha bsnyad med //
NK125(co)005:257: dper na chu la chu thim ltar //
NK125(co)005:258: 'ja' tshon ri mo yal ba la //
NK125(co)005:259: de la 'chi rgyu ga la yod //
NK125(co)005:260: sems la skye 'chi med mod ste //
NK125(co)005:261: 'byung gzhi rnam par dag pa dang //
NK125(co)005:262: sgyu ma'i grong khyer zhig tshul ston //
NK125(co)005:265: rang sems skye ba med pa 'di //
NK125(co)005:266: dag pa'i zhing du 'gro ba la //
NK125(co)005:268: don la 'chi rgyu med mod kyang //
NK125(co)005:269: nga nyid song zhes sgrog pa'i tshe //
NK125(co)005:271: sdug bsngal mya ngan ma byed par //
NK125(co)005:272: nang du rang gi sems la bltos //
NK125(co)005:273: ma bcos rang zhal 'jal ba'i tshe //
NK125(co)005:274: nga dang 'bral ba med pa ste //
NK125(co)005:275: rang gi don gyi bla ma mthong //
NK125(co)005:276: rdzogs chen gnas lugs b+hee pa yang //
NK125(co)005:277: nga dang 'bral ba med pa yin //
NK125(co)005:278: bskyed rims bsgom bzlas byas gyur na //
NK125(co)005:279: nga dang 'bral med ngo bo gcig /
NK125(co)005:280: thun bzhir bla ma'i rnal 'byor bsgom //
NK125(co)005:281: dbang bzhi len zhing mnyam par bzhag /
NK125(co)005:283: dngos po bsog 'dzin ma byed par //
NK125(co)005:284: ci yod 'phral du dge bar thong //
NK125(co)005:285: gang byed chos dang mthun pa na //
NK125(co)005:286: de yang nga dang mjal ba yin //
NK125(co)005:288: de nas lcags pho byi ba'i lo shar ba'i tshe /
NK125(co)005:289: bdag gi bsam par da lo ni gar yang mi 'gro /
NK125(co)005:290: rje drung sku khams bsnyel ba byung na'ang sku rim phyag phyi byed /
NK125(co)005:291: zhing du gshegs pa byung na mi mjal ba 'dug snyam na'ang /
NK125(co)005:292: yang shar phyogs nas 'bod mkhan dos drag byung bas mi 'gro dbang med la gtad /
NK125(co)005:293: 'gro dus byin rlabs zhus te smon btab /
NK125(co)005:294: sku tshe'i rgyal mtshan brtan pa dang /
NK125(co)005:295: thugs dam gyi skyabs 'og tu 'jug par zhu zhus /
NK125(co)005:296: da lo mjal mkhan mang bas thugs so bsod po yang ma byung /
NK125(co)005:297: dgun stod cis kyang sku mtshams dam pa cig ces kyang zhu zhus pas /
NK125(co)005:298: zhal nas de ka byed khyed rang tsho yang myur du yong ba gal che gsung /
NK125(co)005:299: de ltar gsungs kyang phyogs nas grwa btsun 'dus pa rnams chos 'dod kyis gdungs pa dang /
NK125(co)005:300: rje gong nas ni gzhan phan gyi mdzad pa kho na thugs su dgongs pa las /
NK125(co)005:301: mgo yul chos rje drung skyab pa sogs la sems khrid sangs rgyas lag bcangs rnams gnang 'dug /
NK125(co)005:302: chos rje mdo' khra ba sogs skor gcig la ma gcig bka' rgya ma'i khrid bskor gnang gda'/
NK125(co)005:303: der yang ma tshad byin po rnams la /
NK125(co)005:304: bla ma dgongs pa 'dus pa las /
NK125(co)005:305: man ngag snying po gser gyi yang zhun gyi khrid gnang 'dug pa'i tshe /
NK125(co)005:306: cho 'phrul chen po lta'i zla ba hor zla dang po shar ba'i tshe /
NK125(co)005:307: sku grib la brten pa'i gsol thang mi bde bar
NK125(co)005:308: mgul mdzer ba tsam byung 'dug pa'i tshe khrid gzhan
NK125(co)005:309: rnams ni grol / snying po yang zhun ma grol bas gnang pa'i 'khyud du yod pa la /
NK125(co)005:310: zla ba de'i tshes bcu drug gi dus rje ye
NK125(co)005:311: shes 'bum pa'i dus mchod yin pas bzab ma mdzad
NK125(co)005:312: / rgyal ba rnams la mchod pa phul ba bas /
NK125(co)005:313: bla ma lan re tsam mnyes pa phan yon che /
NK125(co)005:315: mchod pa thams cad yongs spangs nas /
NK125(co)005:316: bla ma'i mchod pa yang dag brtsams /
NK125(co)005:318: de las kyang bla ma'i dus mchod 'di rang phan yon che gsung /
NK125(co)005:319: de'i nyin khrid dmigs pa spo rgyu yang yin pas /
NK125(co)005:322: sku khams kyang dngas skyed ma byung ba'i steng du /
NK125(co)005:323: cung zad lod du song 'dug pas 'then pa zab pa 'dra zhus /
NK125(co)005:324: de nas sku khams kyis ma lcogs pas khrid byung gnas 'gro gsum rtsad gcod pa'i skabs su lus /
NK125(co)005:325: de'i dus gtso bor phyag phyi la /
NK125(co)005:330: gzim dpon rnams sku mtshams kyi 'og tu /
NK125(co)005:332: sku rim kyang ci mang du byas /
NK125(co)005:333: mtsho byed jo mo ba gdan 'dren byas /
NK125(co)005:335: gdang bskyed ni ci yang ma byung /
NK125(co)005:336: zhal nas sman dpyad 'di sngar nas kyang 'jug pa cher med /
NK125(co)005:338: da lan rim 'gro yang ngo cher mi 'dug gsung /
NK125(co)005:339: rang rgyud pa bzhin gyi snyung ba dos grag rang mi 'dug na'ang /
NK125(co)005:340: shugs kyis sku dub pa sku shed kyang chung du song nas /
NK125(co)005:341: tshes nyi shu'i nub khong rnams kyis zhus te /
NK125(co)005:342: phyag phyir nyal dgos pa 'dra zhus /
NK125(co)005:343: da lta rang mi dgos zhag lnga tsam nas dgos pa yod gsung /
NK125(co)005:344: de nas zhag gnyis song tshe khong grogs mched rnams kyis sku khams dga' mo mi yong ba 'dra /
NK125(co)005:345: khong dpon slob rnams la mi gcig gnang na mi zab bam zhus pas /
NK125(co)005:346: zhal nas dga' mo yod las che /
NK125(co)005:348: ma byung yang nga ma tshad thams cad mi rtag pa'i mtshan nyid yin /
NK125(co)005:349: khyed rang rnams kyang 'chi ba mi rtag pa sgoms /
NK125(co)005:350: 'khor ba'i chos la zhen pa log par gyis /
NK125(co)005:351: gnas chen dang ri khrod dben pa bsten /
NK125(co)005:352: ngas phog pa'i gdams pa rnams rtse gcig tu nyams su long /
NK125(co)005:353: mi lus chus ma bsan par tshe gcig la sangs rgyas thob par gyis gsung /
NK125(co)005:354: de'i nang par de dbu ma'i rnam pa 'phral mar ldang ba 'dug pas /
NK125(co)005:356: sngar gyi ya ma dang mi 'dra ba 'dug /
NK125(co)005:357: ya ma'i tshul byung dus nga la mthong snang dpag tu med pa yong pa 'dug /
NK125(co)005:358: khyed tshos ma mthong ngom gsung /
NK125(co)005:360: gzigs snang ci 'dra byung zhus pas /
NK125(co)005:361: skabs su zhing khams thams cad mthing khar shar te /
NK125(co)005:363: me tog kyang mthing kha che ba sbra phub tsam chung ba gting phor tsam gyis khengs 'dug cing /
NK125(co)005:364: de dbus lha yang mi bskyod pa sku mdog mthing
NK125(co)005:365: khar bzhugs pa'i snang ba shar te nga rang yang
NK125(co)005:366: 'od khyim der mchongs na bsam pa yong ba 'dug
NK125(co)005:367: gsung / res 'ga' zhing khams me tog 'od khyim thams cad dkar po /
NK125(co)005:368: de dbus rnam snang dkar po /
NK125(co)005:369: de bzhin du zhing khams thams cad ser po /
NK125(co)005:371: ljang khu la sogs shar zhing /
NK125(co)005:373: don yod grus pa rnams gzigs pa dang /
NK125(co)005:374: zhing khams de rnams su phyin na bsam pa'i snang ba shar yong ba 'dug gsung /
NK125(co)005:375: de tsam ma gtogs khong grogs mched rnams kyis kyang
NK125(co)005:376: zhu ma spobs pa 'dra ste 'da' kha zhal chems
NK125(co)005:377: la sogs ni ci yang ma gnang 'dug /
NK125(co)005:378: gzigs snang mkha' 'gro'i bsu ba la sogs kyi ltas dpag med byung tshod 'dug go //
NK125(co)005:379: de'i sang nyi shu lnga'i nyin mtsho byed kyis phyag rtsa phul dus /
NK125(co)005:380: bde mo mi 'dug par rig ste sdug bsngal gyis non /
NK125(co)005:381: snga dro gsol ba gsol ja gsol rag yang cung zad re mchod /
NK125(co)005:382: khong rnams la dgyes pa'i gsung yang 'ga' re gnang 'dug /
NK125(co)005:383: de nas khyed rang tsho yang 'dir 'tshogs nas bsdad mi dgos gsung /
NK125(co)005:384: phyag g.yon pas thugs dam 'dren zhing /
NK125(co)005:385: bskyed rims kyi bsgom bzlas yun ring du mdzad do //
NK125(co)005:387: snang srid snod bcud zhing khams thams cad sbra gur gyi chon thag sdud pa ltar /
NK125(co)005:392: thugs srog yig 'bru mi dmigs pas rgyas 'debs gnang ba dang bstun /
NK125(co)005:393: snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK125(co)005:394: skye 'gag gnas gsum 'gro 'ong gi mtha' thams cad
NK125(co)005:395: dang bral ba 'ub chub blo 'das chen po'i ngang
NK125(co)005:396: du bsdus pa'i rtags su phyag g.yas pas se gol
NK125(co)005:398: de nas 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad dbyer med
NK125(co)005:399: zung 'jug chen po'i brdar phyag gnyis thugs khar bsnol
NK125(co)005:400: te / dgongs pa chos dbyings su thim mo //
NK125(co)005:401: tshad med thugs rje yangs pa'i dkyil 'khor rgyas /
NK125(co)005:402: smin grol bka' drin gsol ba'i 'od 'phros pas /
NK125(co)005:403: mun bsal blo yi pad mo kha phye nas /
NK125(co)005:404: gdul bya'i ri la nye bar nub tshul bstan /
NK125(co)005:405: shes rab mkha' la thab tshogs chu 'dzin 'khrigs /
NK125(co)005:406: spobs pa'i glog 'gyu zab brjid 'brug sgra sgrog /
NK125(co)005:407: gdul bya'i lo thog rgyas mdzad thugs rje'i sprin /
NK125(co)005:408: chos sku'i mkhar dengs mya ngan 'das tshul bstan /
NK125(co)005:411: khong rnams kyis mchod yon rgyun mi 'chad phul /
NK125(co)005:412: bdag ma sleb kyi bar du /
NK125(co)005:413: gsang sgrog dam par byas te /
NK125(co)005:414: rkang mgyogs pa btang byung na'ang /
NK125(co)005:415: bdag sbyin bdag gis gor thebs pas dus la ma thon byung bas /
NK125(co)005:417: nam mkha' la g.ya' dag pa dang /
NK125(co)005:419: sgra dang thug chom bar bir du byung /
NK125(co)005:420: khyad par zhag bzhi song dus thugs dam grol pa'i
NK125(co)005:421: rtags dbu gtsug tu zil pa phrom ye byung 'dug
NK125(co)005:422: dus / khong rnams kyis bzhugs khri stod de /
NK125(co)005:423: nyer dgu'i nyin gdan 'dren zhus pas /
NK125(co)005:424: sa chen po yang rab tu g.yos /
NK125(co)005:426: de nas sku la dar zab longs spyod rdzogs pa'i rgyan gyis mnga' gsol /
NK125(co)005:427: phyag gnyis thugs khar rdo rje dril bu 'dzin par mdzad de bzhugs su gsol /
NK125(co)005:428: dus bzang rnams su gdung la dri bzang 'thul ba dang /
NK125(co)005:429: gsol ba btab pas rtogs pa khyad par can rgyud la skyes zer ro //
NK125(co)005:430: gshegs nas zhag nyer gcig hor zla gnyis pa'i nya'i nub dgongs bdag sku gdung dang mjal /
NK125(co)005:431: de nas zhag gnyis song ba'i tshes bcu bdun gsang brtol /
NK125(co)005:432: gra btsun yon bdag rnams la yur mjal btang bas /
NK125(co)005:433: thams cad sdug bsngal gyi gtson rar tshud /
NK125(co)005:436: gdung shugs kyi smre sngags 'don zhing mchi ma rlag go //
NK125(co)005:438: pad+ma 'byung gnas rgyal tshab nyi ma ste //
NK125(co)005:439: dus kyi rgyal po byi lo shar ba'i tshe //
NK125(co)005:440: cho 'phrul chen po'i zla ba nyer lnga la //
NK125(co)005:441: sangs rgyas nyi ma gdul bya'i snang ngor nub //
NK125(co)005:442: nam mkha' g.ya' dag 'ja' 'od gur du phub //
NK125(co)005:443: sgra dang thub chom sa rnams rab tu g.yos //
NK125(co)005:444: 'gro ba'i nyi ma stag tshang dag tu nub //
NK125(co)005:445: dgos 'dod nor bu chos dbyings rgya mtshor stor //
NK125(co)005:446: shes rab sgron me dus kyi rlung gis bskyod //
NK125(co)005:447: sa'i skrag nyams thar pa'i grong khyer zhig /'di 'dra'i bshes gnyen rnyed par ga la 'gyur /
NK125(co)005:448: mi re'i khong nas snying re bud do rje //
NK125(co)005:449: 'od gsal nyi ma nub par gyur pa la //
NK125(co)005:450: lta ngan mun pa su yis sel nus sam //
NK125(co)005:451: gru chen rgya mtshor zhig par gyur pa la //
NK125(co)005:452: chu bo bzhi las gang gis sgrol bar nus //
NK125(co)005:453: bdag sogs rjes 'jug bla slob gdul bya yi //
NK125(co)005:454: 'phrin las chu rgyun rab tu chad pa la //
NK125(co)005:455: gdul bya'i myug gu gang nas skye bar 'gyur //
NK125(co)005:456: kye hud skye mchog chen po gang du gshegs //
NK125(co)005:457: bdag sogs rjes 'jug bu slob thams cad la //
NK125(co)005:458: rjes su bzung zhing byin gyi brlab tu gsol //
NK125(co)005:459: de nas rang gi bu slob rnams kyis /
NK125(co)005:460: sku gdung gazhu'am bzhugs bsdur bas /
NK125(co)005:462: grwa sgres bsod dbang phyug sogs lho'i bu chen rnams ni /
NK125(co)005:463: gdung bzhugs na gdan sa'i gzhi yin pas /
NK125(co)005:465: sa phyogs dang yul ris su bkra shis pa dang byin rlabs 'byung zer ba 'dug kyang /
NK125(co)005:466: bdag rang gi bsam tshod phyis zhabs tog bsgrub mkhan kyang ci 'dra yong yin /
NK125(co)005:467: rang bya bral gyi tshul mtha' gcig tu ma nges pas bzhus pa legs bsam te /
NK125(co)005:468: thag bcad de nub rang nas gzim khang steng du dkyil 'khor spur khang bzhengs /
NK125(co)005:469: sbyin bsreg mchod pa'i yo byad rnams bsags nas bzhus pa dang /
NK125(co)005:470: nam mkha' g.ya' dag pa dang /
NK125(co)005:471: shar phyogs nas 'ja' dkar rnam bu brkyang pa lta bu zug byung /
NK125(co)005:472: yur ston kyang rgyas par byas /
NK125(co)005:473: de nas zhag nyer gcig gi bar du gtsug lag khang du dge 'dun chog shes rnams bsdus te /
NK125(co)005:474: cho ga mchod 'bul gsol 'debs kyi thugs dam btsugs /
NK125(co)005:475: bdag cag nyung 'dus kyis kyang gdung khang gi sku mdun du mchod 'bul ma chag par byas /
NK125(co)005:476: de dus kyi tho rangs kha gcig la bdag gis bla ma'i rnal 'byor dbang bzhi blangs rjes /
NK125(co)005:477: gnyid du dum tsam song ba'i rmi lam du /
NK125(co)005:478: rje nyid bzhugs khri steng du bzhugs pa gcig mthong
NK125(co)005:479: ste bsam pa la rje zhing du gshegs nas gdung
NK125(co)005:481: da lan mjal byung ba rmi lam yin pa 'dra snyam ste /
NK125(co)005:482: rmi lam 'dzin pa'i 'dun pa yang cung zad byung dus /
NK125(co)005:483: zhal nas sog cus kyi dar yol de nyar cag gyis gsungs pa'i brda' chos cig gnang byung /
NK125(co)005:484: der rjes sku skye bzhes par e gnang zhus pas /
NK125(co)005:485: gsung ba'i grabs gcig la gzhan rkyen gcig gis gnyid sad par gyur /
NK125(co)005:486: de nas cho ga grol te hor zla gsum pa'i tshes brgyad la /
NK125(co)005:487: lho bod kyi grwa slob bu chen thams cad zhus 'bul la de gong du 'dus te /
NK125(co)005:489: rten mchod kyi thog drangs 'bul ba lnga tshan sum tshan sogs byas /
NK125(co)005:490: byin po grwa btsun bzhi brgya tsam 'tshogs pa la /
NK125(co)005:498: dar ras sogs la spyad pa'i stag tshang gi khal re'i rtsis thob par byas so //
NK125(co)005:499: de nas gdung khang bkrol te /
NK125(co)005:500: chos kyi skur thim pa la /
NK125(co)005:501: nam mkha' g.ya' dag pa tsam ma gtogs rten lhag par 'byon par ma bshad na'ang /
NK125(co)005:502: 'on kyang gdul bya rnams mos pa bskyed phyir du rten la /
NK125(co)005:503: gdod nas dag pa'i sku 'gyur med thob pa'i rtags su /
NK125(co)005:504: phyag ngar nas kan tu bzang po'i sku gcig /
NK125(co)005:505: skye ba med pa 'gags med gsung mchog thob pa'i rtags su /
NK125(co)005:506: dbu thod las yi ge a gcig /
NK125(co)005:507: rgyal ba kun dang thugs gnyis su med pa'i rtags su /
NK125(co)005:508: gdung che ba sran ma tsam gcig dang /
NK125(co)005:509: gzhan yang ring srel dpag tu med pa byon no //
NK125(co)005:510: de nas zla ba bzhi pa'i nang du /
NK125(co)005:511: dpon mo che dbang rgyal gdan drangs te /
NK125(co)005:512: gzir mal gyi sku li ma khru gang ba gcig dang /
NK125(co)005:513: gtsug lag khang gi steng du spur khang gi sa
NK125(co)005:514: dang gdung sol rnams las grub pa'i rnam rgyal mchod
NK125(co)005:515: rten thog tshad ma gcig bzhengs te /
NK125(co)005:516: de gnyis kyi nang du sku gdung ring srel yang dpag med bzhugs /
NK125(co)005:517: dpon yang yon gyis mnyes par byas /
NK125(co)005:518: de nas hor zla lnga pa'i nang du bod du yongs te /
NK125(co)005:519: phyi rten byang chub mchod rten thog so gsum pa
NK125(co)005:520: gcig bzhengs te byin brlabs kyi rten yang yang dag
NK125(co)005:521: bzhugs / ngo mtshar gyi ltas gdugs phub tshe gzo
NK125(co)005:522: bo'i nyams la rje rang gi phyag gi snyabs te
NK125(co)005:523: phub pa'i nyams snang byung ba dang /
NK125(co)005:524: 'ja' tshon gyi gur phub me tog gi char bab bo //
NK125(co)005:525: rje'i zla mchod kyi steng du 'bring 'tshams lho byang gi grwa slob rnams la 'gyed skal dang /
NK125(co)005:526: grwa tshang dgon pa dbu rtse rnams su'ang tshogs mang ja 'gyed chas phul lo //
NK125(co)005:527: de nas hor zla drug pa'i nang du ni /
NK125(co)005:528: spyan ras gzigs dbang bod yul mir sprul skye ba yang yang du bzhes pa /
NK125(co)005:529: sku skye ba brgyad pa mi bskyod rdo rje'i drung du /
NK125(co)005:530: rang la gang yod rnams khyer te phyin pas gzhis kha rin dpungs su mjal /
NK125(co)005:531: sku gsung thugs rten phyag dril dung dkar cha /
NK125(co)005:532: yol ba bla bres ting khebs /
NK125(co)005:533: man+dala ting bdun tshar sogs mchod cha tshang ma /
NK125(co)005:534: gsol dkar khro zangs la sogs thab chas tshang ma /
NK125(co)005:535: 'chibs pa nor bu rgyal gyis gtso byas rta pho brgyad /
NK125(co)005:536: g.yu chen bzang ba gcig gis gtso byas g.yu lnga /
NK125(co)005:539: spen 'dog bubs nyi shu la sogs dar ras yug mang ba /
NK125(co)005:540: grwa btsun dpon slob nyis brgya tsam yod de /
NK125(co)005:541: rang gi ras lcags shu gu /
NK125(co)005:542: rnam phrug sogs che yod chung yod sdoms nas phul bas /
NK125(co)005:543: rje chos kyi dbyings su thim pa la mtho dman med mod kyang /
NK125(co)005:544: spyir phan bde'i 'byung gnas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dar zhing rgyas pa dang /
NK125(co)005:545: sems can rnams la bde skyid 'byung ba dang /
NK125(co)005:546: khyad par rje gong nas ni dgongs pa zag med gong nas gong du rdzogs phyir /
NK125(co)005:547: rgyal ba'i dbang po karma pas dbu zhwa 'dzam gling g.yas bzhag bzhes te bsngo ba yang dag gnang /
NK125(co)005:548: rje thams cad mkhyen pa gtsang phyogs su phebs nas
NK125(co)005:549: 'bul ba bzang shos su byung zer ba'i snyan pa
NK125(co)005:550: phyogs bcur khyab par gyur ro //
NK125(co)005:551: de nas ngur smig sgron ma la dkar me brgya phrag tsam phul /
NK125(co)005:552: yar mar gyi lam du chos rje bsod nams mchog
NK125(co)005:553: grub pa sogs nyang stod rong phyogs mgo yul phyogs
NK125(co)005:554: sogs kyi bu chen lhor ma byon pa rnam la
NK125(co)005:555: rang rang gi byin rlabs 'bul 'gyed kyi sku skal
NK125(co)005:556: so sor phul / gnas snying chos sder 'bras tsha dang /
NK125(co)005:557: mkhan po'i drung du sku gsung thugs rten /
NK125(co)005:558: stag gzig gung gsum gyi 'bul ba byas /
NK125(co)005:559: de nas zla ba bdun pa'i nang du la stod
NK125(co)005:560: bar 'grog tu phyin nas khong rnams la tshogs dang
NK125(co)005:562: nang rten gyi zangs rgyu rnams kyang brtson bsgrub 'bad pa ston /
NK125(co)005:563: zla ba brgyad pa'i nang du zar stag nas yongs te /
NK125(co)005:564: byang phug jo bo la gser chab gsol /
NK125(co)005:567: hor zla dgu pa'i nang du 'bring mtshams mgo yul phyogs brgyud nas lhor sleb /
NK125(co)005:568: bod phyogs nas dad 'bul rten bzhengs la phan pa'i dad 'bul kyang yang dag byung /
NK125(co)005:569: de dang mtshungs par bzo rig pa'i gnas la mkhas
NK125(co)005:570: pa bal po lo sku glu sogs bzhi gdan drangs
NK125(co)005:571: te / zla ba bcu pa'i tshes gcig la gzo tshugs /
NK125(co)005:572: lho phyogs nas grwa btsun yon bdag rnams kyis gser
NK125(co)005:573: sogs kyi 'bul ba blos mi 'khyud pa byung ste
NK125(co)005:574: / dpon slob gros su bstun nas /
NK125(co)005:575: o rgyan gyi mkhan po pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi sku
NK125(co)005:576: khams gsum zil mnon du grags pa brgya mtho bcu
NK125(co)005:578: gser 'bum mthong ba don ldan brgya mtho drug pa gcig /
NK125(co)005:579: sku 'dra 'gro don ma gzo phud ma gcig rnams gser zangs las grub pa /
NK125(co)005:580: bal po'i bzo khyad kyis mngon par mtho ba /
NK125(co)005:581: glang lo zla ba dang po'i khongs su sku che ba grub cing /
NK125(co)005:582: dus mchod chen mo yang shin tu bzab par byas /
NK125(co)005:583: yongs su dril ba'i rab gnas dngos gzhi /
NK125(co)005:584: zla ba gnyis pa'i tshes nyi shu la gtsugs te /
NK125(co)005:585: dga' ston bkra shis rnams nyer lnga tshun la grub par bgyis so //
NK125(co)005:586: bal po rnams yon rdzongs kyis mnyes par byas /
NK125(co)005:587: zhib tu dkar chag kyi nang du gsal /
NK125(co)005:588: de nas gser lhag rta dang dngul spyad lcags dang dar ras sogs gang yod rnams /
NK125(co)005:589: bon po bsod nams ye shes grogs mched la bskur te /
NK125(co)005:590: lha sa jo sh+aaka drung du gser chab dkar me
NK125(co)005:591: snyan dar 'bul ba sogs gser ston rgyas pa byas
NK125(co)005:592: 'dug / dpal gyi bsam yas su dkar me rgyu
NK125(co)005:593: snum nag gtso che ba mar khal brgya'i rtsis phul
NK125(co)005:595: dge ba'i stobs shin tu rgya che ba 'grub bo //
NK125(co)005:596: dkar po ba rab 'byams pa la'ang rta pho bzang ba gcig gis gtsos pa'i lnga tshan tsam phul /
NK125(co)005:597: de bar bdag rnams kyis rgyu dngos gang 'dug rnams lhag lus med par byed snyam ste /
NK125(co)005:599: ma ni dung phyur gcig re zhig btang dgos bsam zhing /
NK125(co)005:600: rje zhal bzhugs pa'i dus kyang dgongs pa ma ni la mnyes pa yod pas /
NK125(co)005:601: dge 'dun brgya tsam la dung phyur btang ste /
NK125(co)005:602: zhabs tog 'bul ba gya nom pa byas kun mnyes par gyur to //
NK125(co)005:603: de nas bod du yongs te /
NK125(co)005:607: chos mdzad chos rgyal ba sogs kyis /
NK125(co)005:608: la stod man 'bring mtshams yan gyi grwa slob rnams kyis /
NK125(co)005:609: gu ru mtsho skyes rdo rje'i sku rgya mtho drug pa gcig dang /
NK125(co)005:610: sku 'dra rnams gser zangs la grub pa /
NK125(co)005:611: sprul sku stag rtse ba gdan drangs te bzhengs su gsol /
NK125(co)005:612: bdag rnams kyis kyang chos rje ri lung sbug pa dang /
NK125(co)005:613: sprul sku ting kheb pa rnams spyan drangs te /
NK125(co)005:614: chos sdings mchod khang du zhing khams bac+wo lnga tsam bzhengs /
NK125(co)005:615: rab gnas dus mtshungs su zla ba bdun pa'i nyer bdun la byas te /
NK125(co)005:616: gnam gang tshun dga' ston dang bcas pa grub bo //
NK125(co)005:617: rgyas par dkar chag nas mtshon no //
NK125(co)005:618: sprul sku rnams sor sor yon gyis mnyes par byas /
NK125(co)005:619: de yan zla mchod kyang gzhi byes gang du'ang ma chag go //
NK125(co)005:620: da dung kyang rang gi ci yod thams cad bla ma'i dgongs pa rdzogs thabs /
NK125(co)005:621: rang gi tshogs bsag sgrib sbyangs kho na bgyid bsam pa'i 'dun pa drag po 'chis so //
NK125(co)005:622: rje'i dgongs rdzogs rnams kyang re zhig mthar thon no //
NK125(co)005:623: kye ma byi lo hor zla dang po'i nyer lnga la //
NK125(co)005:624: 'dren mchog dam pa chos kyi dbyings su thim //
NK125(co)005:625: de nas bzung ste glang lo zla ba ni //
NK125(co)005:626: bdun pa man du bdag sogs rjes 'jug gis //
NK125(co)005:627: dgongs rdzogs zla mchod 'bul bgyis rten bzhengs grub //
NK125(co)005:628: legs pa bgyis pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba 'dis //
NK125(co)005:629: dpal ldan bla ma'i dgongs pa rdzogs pa dang //
NK125(co)005:630: rjes 'jug rnams kyis tshogs bsags sgrib byang nas //
NK125(co)005:631: kun kyang dkyil 'khor gcig tu 'grub pa shog /
NK125(co)005:632: e ma gdod nas rnam dag rgya mtsho chen po la //
NK125(co)005:633: sku gsum yon tan phrin las gting mtha' zab //
NK125(co)005:634: bdag blo rmongs pas rtogs par ga la 'gyur //
NK125(co)005:635: 'on kyang dad mos gdung shugs drag po yis //
NK125(co)005:636: mya ngan 'das pa'i rnam thar chu thig tsam //
NK125(co)005:637: blang ba'i dge bas mkha' mnyam 'gro ba kun //
NK125(co)005:638: kun bzang bla ma'i go 'phangs myur thob shog /
NK125(co)005:639: zhes pa 'di nyid kho bo rnam grol ye shes bzang pos /
NK125(co)005:640: dpal 'bras mo bshongs kyi nub sgo gangs chen mdzod lnga stag rtse'i zhol /
NK125(co)005:641: dge rgyas 'jag ma lung gi phu /
NK125(co)005:642: dge legs sman bzang gi mdun du sbyar ba 'di dge legs su gyur cig //
